    <title>Health Care Sharing Fairness Act</title>
    <createDate>2017-11-22T12:17:52Z</createDate>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2018-06-04T14:24:49Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Health Care Sharing Fairness Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a deduction for amounts paid as a member of a health care sharing ministry for: (1) the sharing of the medical expenses of fellow members, and (2) administrative fees of the health care sharing ministry. </p>]]></text>
